<lb n="0159b03" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1229</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0159b04" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0159022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note><title>穢跡金剛<note n="0159023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（法）＋禁【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（法）＋禁【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159023"><lem>禁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">法禁</rdg></app>百變<note n="0159024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">法＋（門）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法＋（門）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159024"><lem>法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">法門</rdg></app><note n="0159025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔經一卷〕－【宋】</note><note n="0159025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔經〕－【宋】</note><app n="0159025"><lem>經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&lac;</rdg></app></title><note n="0159026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【元】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0159026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159026"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0159b05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0159b06" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0159027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔北天竺國〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔北天竺國〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159027"><lem>北天竺國</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>三藏沙門阿質
<lb n="0159b07" ed="T"/>達霰<note n="0159028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔唐言無能勝將〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔唐言無能勝將〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159028"><lem>唐言無能勝將</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0159b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0159b0801">爾時金剛復白佛言。世尊若有善男子善女
<lb n="0159b09" ed="T"/>人。持我此&CB00057;無&CB00283;驗者無有是處。欲令山摧
<lb n="0159b10" ed="T"/>者。取白芥子三升上好安<note n="0159029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悉＝息【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0159029"><lem>悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">息</rdg></app>香。於山中疑有
<lb n="0159b11" ed="T"/><note n="0159030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寶＋（處）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶＋（處）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159030"><lem>寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">寶處</rdg></app>。取<note n="0159031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鑌＝賓【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鑌＝賓【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159031"><lem>鑌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">賓</rdg></app>鐵刀一枚。畫四方為界。<note n="0159032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">耳＝取【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耳＝取【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159032"><lem>耳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">取</rdg></app>淨巾
<lb n="0159b12" ed="T"/>一枚香爐一枚。燒安<app source="0159029" type="＊"><lem>悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">息</rdg></app>香先&CB00057;一千八遍。取
<lb n="0159b13" ed="T"/>白芥子四散<note n="0159033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">及＝乃【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及＝乃【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159033"><lem>及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">乃</rdg></app>至七遍。作是法其山自摧。若
<lb n="0159b14" ed="T"/>有寶之處其藏神捨寶而出任意用之。若欲
<lb n="0159b15" ed="T"/>令海竭者。先&CB00057;一千八遍。以金銅作一龍形。
<lb n="0159b16" ed="T"/>擲於海中即時海竭。若欲令江河逆流者。取
<lb n="0159b17" ed="T"/>安<app source="0159029" type="＊"><lem>悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">息</rdg></app>香作一象形。無問大小擲水中&CB00057;一百
<lb n="0159b18" ed="T"/>八遍。<note n="0159034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">登＝即&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159034"><lem>登</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">即</rdg></app>時逆流。令依舊者&CB00057;一淨石擲之
<lb n="0159b19" ed="T"/>水中其水如故。若有雷電霹靂毒龍卒風惡
<lb n="0159b20" ed="T"/>雨者。即作止雷<note n="0159035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">電＝雹【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">電＝雹【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159035"><lem>電</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">雹</rdg></app>印。以左手中指無名指
<lb n="0159b21" ed="T"/>小指並屈掌中。<note n="0159036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（直）&M062403;＋頭【甲】</note><app n="0159036"><lem>頭</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">直頭</rdg></app>指以大<note n="0159037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">母＝拇【三】【甲】下同</note><note n="0159037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">母＝拇【宋】【元】【明】【甲】下同</note><app n="0159037"><lem>母</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">拇</rdg></app>指。捻頭指中
<lb n="0159b22" ed="T"/>節上。誦&CB00057;&CB00057;之。以印遙指雷雹之處自止。
<lb n="0159b23" ed="T"/>若欲令一切鬼神自來歸伏為給使者。取水
<lb n="0159b24" ed="T"/>三<note n="0159038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">斗＝升【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斗＝升【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159038"><lem>斗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">升</rdg></app>盛銅器中。以淨灰圍之。即作<note n="0159039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">教＝都【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">教＝都【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159039"><lem>教</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">都</rdg></app>攝錄
<lb n="0159b25" ed="T"/>印。以二無名指並屈掌中。令背相倚。二中
<lb n="0159b26" ed="T"/>指頭相捻。二頭指及小指各如開華。以大母
<lb n="0159b27" ed="T"/>指<note n="0159040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">捻＋（頭指）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">捻＋（頭指）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159040"><lem>捻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">捻頭指</rdg></app>中節。默&CB00057;一百八遍。其世界內所有
<lb n="0159b28" ed="T"/>諸惡鬼。並來雲集自現其身。捨毒惡心任行
<lb n="0159b29" ed="T"/>人驅<note n="0159041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">使＋（若有百鳥與人作怪者即向鳥作怪之處誦明一百八遍其鳥自來而死）&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159041"><lem>使</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">使若有百鳥與人作怪者即向鳥作怪之處誦明一百八遍其鳥自來而死</rdg></app>。若禁山者所至之山。誦&CB00057;百遍大
<pb n="0159c" id="T21.1229.0159c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0159c01" ed="T"/>叫三聲。即作<note n="0159042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔業山〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔業山〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159042"><lem>業山</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>印以<note n="0159043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">右＝左&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159043"><lem>右</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">左</rdg></app>手無名<note n="0159044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">指＋（小指）【甲】</note><app n="0159044"><lem>指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">指小指</rdg></app>。屈
<lb n="0159c02" ed="T"/>於掌中。直&CB00594;中頭大<note n="0159045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">母等指＝拇指等【甲】</note><app n="0159045"><lem>母等指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">拇指等</rdg></app>。並直&CB00594;。向<note n="0159046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＝山【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上＝山【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159046"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">山</rdg></app>
<lb n="0159c03" ed="T"/>印之七遍。即&CB00230;行七步。<note n="0159047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">後＝復&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0159047"><lem>後</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">復</rdg></app>七<note n="0159048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝即【三】</note><note n="0159048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印＝即【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0159048"><lem>印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">即</rdg></app>山。<note n="0159049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔其山中〕&M062403;－【甲】</note><app n="0159049"><lem>其
<lb n="0159c04" ed="T"/>山中</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>即一切鳥<note n="0159050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">狩＝獸【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狩＝獸【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159050"><lem>狩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">獸</rdg></app>並移出山。若作此印&CB00057;七
<lb n="0159c05" ed="T"/>遍。以印向空中印三七度。其空中毫塵不
<lb n="0159c06" ed="T"/><note n="0159051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">過＝遇【三】</note><note n="0159051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＝遇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0159051"><lem>過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">遇</rdg></app>。若欲令人不語者。<note n="0159052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">書＝畫【三】</note><note n="0159052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">書＝畫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0159052"><lem>書</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">畫</rdg></app>前人姓名。向口
<lb n="0159c07" ed="T"/>中含<note n="0159053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">口＝之【三】【甲】</note><note n="0159053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">口＝之【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0159053"><lem>口</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">之</rdg></app>。其人口不<note n="0159054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">能＝離【宋】【元】</note><app n="0159054"><lem>能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">離</rdg></app>言。吐出即語得。若誦
<lb n="0159c08" ed="T"/>一切諸&CB00057;先須作壇。若誦我此&CB00057;者即勿須
<lb n="0159c09" ed="T"/>作壇。但剋一跋枳金剛<note n="0159055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">榼＝猛【甲】</note><app n="0159055"><lem>榼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">猛</rdg></app>杵。於佛塔中或
<lb n="0159c10" ed="T"/>於靜室中。用香泥塗地隨其大小。著種種香
<lb n="0159c11" ed="T"/>華供養。安杵壇中&CB00057;一百八遍。其杵即自動。
<lb n="0159c12" ed="T"/>或變作種種異物亦勿怪之。更誦&CB00057;一百八
<lb n="0159c13" ed="T"/>遍。其杵自去地三尺以來。或五六七尺乃至
<lb n="0159c14" ed="T"/>一丈以來。持法之人即須歸依懺悔發願。我
<lb n="0159c15" ed="T"/>於彼中即現真身。隨行人意所願樂者。並皆
<lb n="0159c16" ed="T"/>速得如意。我即與授菩提之記。即得身心解
<lb n="0159c17" ed="T"/>脫。先須誦十萬遍滿。然後作法若課未充不
<lb n="0159c18" ed="T"/>得&CB00283;驗。</p>
<pb n="0160a" id="T21.1229.0160a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a01" ed="T"/><div2 type="other"><head>印法第二</head>
<lb n="0160a02" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160a0201"><note n="0160001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麗本印圖總無之今依明本載之</note>印<figure entity="FigT21016001"/>此印方一寸八分<note n="0160002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">刻＝剋【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0160002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">刻＝剋【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0160002"><lem>刻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">剋</rdg></app>之。&CB00057;
<lb n="0160a03" ed="T"/>一千遍。<note n="0160003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">日＝用【三】【甲】</note><note n="0160003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日＝用【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0160003"><lem>日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">用</rdg></app>白膠香度之。剋
<lb n="0160a04" ed="T"/>印日勿令人見。用印印心。得
<lb n="0160a05" ed="T"/>心智自然智宿命智。持印百
<lb n="0160a06" ed="T"/>日。即<note n="0160004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得住＝任得【甲】</note><app n="0160004"><lem>得<note n="0160005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">住＝任【三】</note><note n="0160005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">住＝任【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0160005"><lem>住</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">任</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">任得</rdg></app>種種大法<note n="0160006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門＋（也）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0160006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">門＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0160006"><lem>門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">門也</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0160a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160a0701">印<figure entity="FigT21016002"/>方一寸二分&CB00057;六百遍。以安
<lb n="0160a08" ed="T"/><note n="0160007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悉＝息【明】【甲】</note><app n="0160007"><lem>悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">息</rdg></app>香度之。帶行令一切人愛
<lb n="0160a09" ed="T"/>樂<note n="0160008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔得〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0160008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔得〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0160008"><lem>得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>大自在永離眾苦。</p>
<lb n="0160a10" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160a1001">印<figure entity="FigT21016003"/>方一寸五分<app source="0160002" type="＊"><lem>刻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">剋</rdg></app>之。&CB00057;六百
<lb n="0160a11" ed="T"/>遍。以白膠香度之。用印印
<lb n="0160a12" ed="T"/>&CB00560;。便得飛騰<note n="0160009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔虛〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0160009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔虛〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0160009"><lem>虛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>空所向自
<lb n="0160a13" ed="T"/>在。</p>
<lb n="0160a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160a1401">印<figure entity="FigT21016004"/>方一寸八分<app source="0160002" type="＊"><lem>刻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">剋</rdg></app>之。用白膠香
<lb n="0160a15" ed="T"/>度之。&CB00057;七千遍。用印印足。可
<lb n="0160a16" ed="T"/>日行三百萬里無人得見。</p></div2>
<lb n="0160a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a18" ed="T"/><div2 type="other"><head><note n="0160010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">神變延命法五字麗本無之今依明本補載之</note>神變延命法</head>
<lb n="0160a19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a20" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160a2001">印<figure entity="FigT21016005"/>伏連。書心上即差。大吉急急
<lb n="0160a21" ed="T"/>如律令。</p>
<lb n="0160a22" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160a2301">印<figure entity="FigT21016006"/>心<note n="0160011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">痛＝為【三】【甲】，病&M062485;【甲】</note><note n="0160011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">痛＝為【宋】【元】【明】【甲】，＝病&M062485;【甲】</note><app n="0160011"><lem><sic resp="【甲】" corr="病">痛</sic></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">為</rdg></app>。書之立即除差。大吉
<lb n="0160a24" ed="T"/>利急急如律令先&CB00057;七遍。</p>
<lb n="0160a25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160a2701"><note n="0160012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以下至印法終麗本無之今依明本補載之</note><figure entity="FigT21016007"/>鬼病。朱書吞之。<figure entity="FigT21016008"/>精魅鬼病之人。朱吞之七大書枚立瘥神驗。</p>
<lb n="0160a28" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160a29" ed="T"/>
<pb n="0160b" id="T21.1229.0160b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160b0101"><figure entity="FigT21016009"/>若<note n="0160013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">依＝作【宋】</note><app n="0160013"><lem>依</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">作</rdg></app>法之人。取白檀綾二
<lb n="0160b02" ed="T"/>丈一尺七寸。白練裹之。置
<lb n="0160b03" ed="T"/>於地輪世界。令人延年得
<lb n="0160b04" ed="T"/>七十歲。若無人送者。即安
<lb n="0160b05" ed="T"/>自宅中庭。掘地七尺埋之
<lb n="0160b06" ed="T"/>亦得。又得聰明多智辯才
<lb n="0160b07" ed="T"/>無礙。</p>
<lb n="0160b08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160b0801">
<lb n="0160b09" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21016010"/><figure entity="FigT21016011"/><figure entity="FigT21016012"/></p>
<lb n="0160b10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160b1101">
<lb n="0160b12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b13" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21016013"/><figure entity="FigT21016014"/><figure entity="FigT21016015"/></p>
<lb n="0160b14" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160b1601"><figure entity="FigT21016016"/>此七道亦能治萬病。吞之亦
<lb n="0160b17" ed="T"/>令人長壽益智大神驗。</p>
<lb n="0160b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160b1801">
<lb n="0160b19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b20" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21016017"/><figure entity="FigT21016018"/><figure entity="FigT21016019"/></p>
<lb n="0160b21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160b2201">
<lb n="0160b23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b24" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21016020"/><figure entity="FigT21016021"/><figure entity="FigT21016022"/></p>
<lb n="0160b25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160b27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160b2701"><figure entity="FigT21016023"/>此上七道用朱書紙上。吞之
<lb n="0160b28" ed="T"/>千枚令人延年。即得與天地
<lb n="0160b29" ed="T"/>齊壽。不得令人見之。</p>
<pb n="0160c" id="T21.1229.0160c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160c0101">
<lb n="0160c02" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21016024"/><figure entity="FigT21016025"/><figure entity="FigT21016026"/></p>
<lb n="0160c03" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c04" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160c0401">
<lb n="0160c05" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21016027"/><figure entity="FigT21016028"/><figure entity="FigT21016029"/></p>
<lb n="0160c06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160c0701"><figure entity="FigT21016030"/>此上七道若有人患一切病。
<lb n="0160c08" ed="T"/>以此符書之皆得除瘥。若人
<lb n="0160c09" ed="T"/>書符吞之者。延年益智大驗
<lb n="0160c10" ed="T"/>&CB00283;矣。</p>
<lb n="0160c11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160c1101">
<lb n="0160c12" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21016031"/><figure entity="FigT21016032"/><figure entity="FigT21016033"/></p>
<lb n="0160c13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160c1401">
<lb n="0160c15" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21016034"/><figure entity="FigT21016035"/><figure entity="FigT21016036"/></p>
<lb n="0160c16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c17" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160c1701"><figure entity="FigT21016037"/>此上七道若有人求種種珍寶
<lb n="0160c18" ed="T"/>者。以朱書此符吞之滿七日。
<lb n="0160c19" ed="T"/>即有種種妙寶自然而至。若
<lb n="0160c20" ed="T"/>求他人財物。當書彼人姓名
<lb n="0160c21" ed="T"/>於符下。其人立即送物到。</p>
<lb n="0160c22" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160c2201">
<lb n="0160c23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c24" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21016038"/><figure entity="FigT21016039"/><figure entity="FigT21016040"/></p>
<lb n="0160c25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0160c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0160c2701">此上三符朱書床四&CB00560;上。常有八大金剛
<lb n="0160c28" ed="T"/>衛護<note n="0160014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悉＝時&M062485;【甲】</note><sic n="0160014" resp="【甲】" corr="時">悉</sic>不暫捨。惟須嚴淨勿令污染之物
<lb n="0160c29" ed="T"/>入房。切須慎之。</p>
<pb n="0161a" id="T21.1229.0161a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0161a0101"><figure entity="FigT21016101"/>有大火災起者。書符擲一枚
<lb n="0161a02" ed="T"/>&CB00057;一百八遍。向火中須臾災
<lb n="0161a03" ed="T"/>自滅。</p>
<lb n="0161a04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0161a0501"><figure entity="FigT21016102"/><note n="0161001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">火＝大【元】</note><app n="0161001"><lem>火</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">大</rdg></app>惡風起者。書此符&CB00057;一
<lb n="0161a06" ed="T"/>百八遍。擲向風中即止。</p>
<lb n="0161a07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a08" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0161a0801"><figure entity="FigT21016103"/>有大水起者。書此符擲於水
<lb n="0161a09" ed="T"/>中。立即斷流水不溺人矣。</p>
<lb n="0161a10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a11" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0161a1101"><figure entity="FigT21016104"/>有大雨者。書此符&CB00057;之一百
<lb n="0161a12" ed="T"/>八遍。向雨擲之其雨立即自
<lb n="0161a13" ed="T"/>定之。</p>
<lb n="0161a14" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0161a1401">
<lb n="0161a15" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a16" ed="T"/><figure entity="FigT21016105"/><figure entity="FigT21016106"/></p>
<lb n="0161a17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a18" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161a19" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0161a1901">此符朱書吞三枚。<note n="0161002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">及＝乃&M062485;【甲】</note><sic n="0161002" resp="【甲】" corr="乃">及</sic>可與他人書符。
<lb n="0161a20" ed="T"/>即有驗&CB00283;。若不爾者用諸符無驗。</p>
<lb n="0161a21" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0161a2101">爾時穢跡金剛說此符已。大眾同聲讚言。善
<lb n="0161a22" ed="T"/>哉大力士汝能說是大妙之法。令諸眾生皆
<lb n="0161a23" ed="T"/>得解脫。爾時金剛頃白諸大眾。當知我於汝
<lb n="0161a24" ed="T"/>等。此法若流行之處。我等大<note n="0161003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天＝夭【宋】【元】</note><app n="0161003"><lem>天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">夭</rdg></app>常當護此行
<lb n="0161a25" ed="T"/>法之人助令成就。是時金剛復作是言。若有
<lb n="0161a26" ed="T"/>眾生行此法者。我即往彼現其人前。所求<note n="0161004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">願＝之【宋】【元】</note><app n="0161004"><lem>願</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">之</rdg></app>
<lb n="0161a27" ed="T"/>者我亦施與。令彼得種種變現種種神通所
<lb n="0161a28" ed="T"/>作無礙。常須念我本師釋迦牟尼佛。我即常
<lb n="0161a29" ed="T"/>隨逐之。令一切法皆助成就。爾時金剛說此
<pb n="0161b" id="T21.1229.0161b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0161b01" ed="T"/>法已。大眾倍加悲喜。及諸天龍大鬼神等。各
<lb n="0161b02" ed="T"/>奉聖言禮足而去。</p></div2>
<lb n="0161b03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><title>穢跡金剛<note n="0161005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（法）＋禁【三】</note><note n="0161005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（法）＋禁【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0161005"><lem>禁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">法禁</rdg></app>百<note n="0161006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">變＋（法門）【明】</note><app n="0161006"><lem>變</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">變法門</rdg></app>經</title><note n="0161007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【三】</note><note n="0161007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0161007"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0161b04" ed="T"/><note n="0161008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔古經…訶〕六行－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0161008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔古經…訶〕六行八十一字－【宋】【元】</note><app word-count="81" n="0161008"><lem><p id="pT21p0161b0423" type="W"><note place="inline">古經本&CB00057;四十三字。唐太宗朝人多持誦感驗非一。除去十字今就錄出。速獲靈應無過是&CB00057;</note>。</p>
<lb n="0161b05" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0161b0501" type="W">唵&CB03117;咶　啒&CB03116;摩訶般囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　很那&CB04237;　吻汁
